<item>
            <title>[AMQ-4798] Destination limit for advisory topic very high after recent commit</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-4798</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;10:58:42&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 gtully on last amq from ASF i see this when starting the standalone broker&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;10:58:43&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 INFO | Usage(default:memory:topic://ActiveMQ.Advisory.MasterBroker:memory) limit=720332416 should be smaller than its parent limit=720332390&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;10:58:54&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 i guess its the recent 70% heap memory stuff&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;10:59:11&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 just wonder if everyone will see this, and if we can make the message more friendly?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:28:06&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;rajdavies&amp;gt;	 davsclaus - why is the destination memory limit so high for an advisory ?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:29:23&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 rajdavies not sure - gtully changed the default settings yesterday instead of fixed 64mb limit etc&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:29:31&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 it was 70% heap memory based instead&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:30:03&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;dejanb&amp;gt;	 rajdavies: and per destination limit is removed &#8230; so I guess we have some bug in there&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:30:06&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;davsclaus&amp;gt;	 &lt;a href=&quot;http://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf/activemq/commit/5bdcc196&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf/activemq/commit/5bdcc196&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;11:30:39&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;rajdavies&amp;gt;	 davsclaus - ok - looks like a bug then&lt;/p&gt;</description>
